name: Damask Dog Collar
description:
The Damask Dog Collar features a geometric design in blue and pink. 

All our collars are handmade with 100% designer cotton fabric that is lined with heavy duty interfacing and high quality Nylon Webbing for extra strength and durability. We take pride in making sure each collar is extremely well made and strong enough to handle any dog big or small!

Our collars come standard with:

- Black YKK plastic contour side release buckles
- Black triglide sliders
- Heavy duty welded Dee Rings
- Triple stitching at stress points for added security

Because of the different designs on some of our fabric, the dog collar you receive may not look exactly as pictured on this listing but very similar depending on the fabric.


Please Refer to the Sizing Guide before ordering you Dog Collar:

SIZES:
X-Small (5/8” width) 7” – 12”
Small (5/8” width) 9” – 15”
Medium (3/4” width) 12” – 19”
Large (1” width) 15” – 25”

Since all of my items are made to order and I do not keep any pre-made inventory please allow 5-7 BUSINESS days (Monday-Friday) to ship your custom collar out. Postal Holidays and Weekends are not included in my turnaround time. Make sure to indicate which size you are ordering at checkout! If you would like a different size/width combination please feel free to include this information at checkout also!
